49
00:02:10,739 --> 00:02:12,828
Better?

50
00:02:12,871 --> 00:02:15,744
<i>Come on.
You can do this, girl.</i>

51
00:02:15,787 --> 00:02:18,050
<i>♪ If I pitch, can you catch...</i>

52
00:02:18,094 --> 00:02:20,183
Strike one.

53
00:02:20,227 --> 00:02:21,924
You can do it, sweetheart.

54
00:02:21,967 --> 00:02:24,492
Strike two.

55
00:02:24,535 --> 00:02:25,928
UMPIRE: Strike three.

56
00:02:25,971 --> 00:02:28,191
I still think you can do it,
sweetheart.

57
00:02:28,235 --> 00:02:29,975
UMPIRE: Strike one.

58
00:02:30,019 --> 00:02:31,934
Strike two.

59
00:02:34,241 --> 00:02:36,243
<i>Strike three.
You're out.</i>

60
00:02:36,286 --> 00:02:38,114
Strike one.

